data.description: PRICE REDUCTION. Excellent opportunity to own a charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home. Set in a delightful family-friendly neighborhood, this residence offers a cozy retreat with a touch of modern convenience. This unit provides an open floor plan, newer stainless steel appliances in the kitchen and spacious living room with direct patio access.   Milano community unfolds with amenities that add a special touch to your lifestyle. Engage in a friendly game on the tennis courts, shoot some hoops on the basketball court, or unwind by the inviting lap pool and hot tub. There's even a dedicated dog park, reflecting the community's commitment to every member of your family, furry friends included. 2023 A/C, 2019 water heater.  Conveniently located near I-75, shopping, and dining, this townhome offers more than just a residence; it offers a lifestyle tailored for ease and accessibility. Top-notch schools, friendly neighbors, and nearby conveniences make this residence a perfect blend of comfort and location.
